query: SELECT e.id, e.evaluationDate, gp.name as gpName, gp.teamId, t.teamName FROM evaluations e LEFT JOIN game_presenters gp ON e.gamePresenterId = gp.id LEFT JOIN fm_teams t ON gp.teamId = t.id ORDER BY e.evaluationDate DESC LIMIT 20;
